description:
My first Textual Inversion embedding!
Download the file and place it in the stable-diffusion-webui\embeddings folder.

The previews are done in: s1dlxbrew_01LOL (https://civitai.com/models/4717/s1dlxbrew)

Add bs_swaisy in your prompt to use her.

Trained on SD 1.5 so will only work with 1.5 models.

Shout out to https://civitai.com/user/dddokter and Scruffy and rockerBOO over at the Civitai discord for the help!
